---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro"
import Breadcrumb from "@/components/Breadcrumb.astro"
---

<Layout title="Sobre mí — Pharloom Archives">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 pt-8 pb-16">
    <Breadcrumb
      crumbs={[{ href: "/", label: "Inicio" }, { label: "Sobre mí" }]}
    />

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="relative card overflow-hidden p-8 md:p-12 mt-4 mb-8">
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-20 -top-20 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-(--color-accent-glow) blur-3xl"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute -left-10 -bottom-10 h-48 w-48 rounded-full bg-(--color-accent-glow) blur-3xl opacity-50"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
      </div>

      <div
        class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-8"
      >
        <div
          class="shrink-0 h-28 w-28 rounded-2xl border border-(--color-accent)/20 bg-(--color-accent-glow) flex items-center justify-center"
        >
          <!-- <svg
            class="h-12 w-12 text-(--color-accent)"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z"
            ></path>
          </svg> -->
          <img
            src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1776312145816227840/ISlE225__400x400.jpg"
            alt="me"
            class="h-16 w-16 rounded-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>

        <div>
          <p
            class="font-[Cinzel] text-[0.7rem] tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-(--color-accent) opacity-60 mb-2"
          >
            El autor
          </p>
          <h1 class="font-[Cinzel] text-3xl md:text-4xl text-(--color-ink)">
            Gergi
          </h1>
          <p
            class="mt-2 text-(--color-ink-muted) text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-lg"
          >
            Fan de Hollow Knight desde el día uno · Constructor de wikis ·
            Jugador compulsivo
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span
              class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-(--color-accent)/30 text-(--color-accent) bg-(--color-accent-glow)"
              >Fan de la chamba</span
            >
            <span
              class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 text-(--color-ink-muted) bg-white/[0.02]"
              >Español</span
            >
            <span
              class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 text-(--color-ink-muted) bg-white/[0.02]"
              >Wiki no oficial</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-6">
        <div class="card p-6">
          <h2 class="font-[Cinzel] text-xl text-(--color-ink) mb-1">
            ¿Por qué esta wiki?
          </h2>
          <div class="h-px w-12 bg-(--color-accent) opacity-25 mb-4"></div>
          <div
            class="space-y-3 text-(--color-ink-muted) text-sm leading-relaxed"
          >
            <p>
              Cuando comencé a jugar me di cuenta de que hacia falta una wiki en
              español que recopilara toda la información del juego de manera
              clara y accesible. Quería crear un recurso que no solo fuera útil
              para los jugadores hispanohablantes, sino que también reflejara mi
              pasión por el juego y mi deseo de compartir ese conocimiento con
              la comunidad.
            </p>
            <p>Uno para todos - y todos para uno.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <h2 class="font-[Cinzel] text-xl text-(--color-ink) mb-1">
            Sobre el proyecto
          </h2>
          <div class="h-px w-12 bg-(--color-accent) opacity-25 mb-4"></div>
          <div
            class="space-y-3 text-(--color-ink-muted) text-sm leading-relaxed"
          >
            <p>
              Esta wiki está construida con
              <strong class="text-(--color-ink)">Astro</strong> y
              <strong class="text-(--color-ink)">Tailwind CSS</strong>, con toda
              la información traducida al español y organizada para que sea
              fácil de navegar.
            </p>
            <p>
              El contenido se actualiza de forma manual conforme se va
              conociendo más del juego. Si encuentras algún error o quieres
              contribuir, no dudes en contactarme.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Columna lateral -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="card p-5">
          <h3
            class="font-[Cinzel] text-sm text-(--color-ink) mb-1 tracking-wide"
          >
            La wiki en números
          </h3>
          <div class="h-px w-8 bg-(--color-accent) opacity-25 mb-4"></div>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {
              [
                { n: "33", label: "Jefes documentados" },
                { n: "20", label: "Instrumentos" },
                { n: "4", label: "Secciones" },
                { n: "∞", label: "Horas jugadas" },
              ].map(({ n, label }) => (
                <li class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-sm text-(--color-ink-muted)">{label}</span>
                  <span class="font-[Cinzel] text-lg text-(--color-accent)">
                    {n}
                  </span>
                </li>
              ))
            }
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-5">
          <h3
            class="font-[Cinzel] text-sm text-(--color-ink) mb-1 tracking-wide"
          >
            Hecho con
          </h3>
          <div class="h-px w-8 bg-(--color-accent) opacity-25 mb-4"></div>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            {
              [
                {
                  label: "Astro",
                  desc: "Framework",
                  href: "https://astro.build",
                },
                {
                  label: "Tailwind CSS",
                  desc: "Estilos",
                  href: "https://tailwindcss.com",
                },
                {
                  label: "TypeScript",
                  desc: "Tipado",
                  href: "https://www.typescriptlang.org",
                },
                {
                  label: "Markdown",
                  desc: "Contenido",
                  href: "https://www.markdownguide.org",
                },
              ].map(({ label, desc, href }) => (
                <li>
                  <a
                    href={href}
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg px-2 py-1.5 hover:bg-white/[0.03] transition group"
                  >
                    <span class="text-sm text-(--color-ink) group-hover:text-(--color-accent) transition">
                      {label}
                    </span>
                    <span class="text-[11px] text-(--color-ink-muted)">
                      {desc} ↗
                    </span>
                  </a>
                </li>
              ))
            }
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-5">
          <h3
            class="font-[Cinzel] text-sm text-(--color-ink) mb-1 tracking-wide"
          >
            Contacto
          </h3>
          <div class="h-px w-8 bg-(--color-accent) opacity-25 mb-4"></div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/AdrianGerman"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] px-3 py-2 text-xs text-(--color-ink-muted) hover:text-(--color-ink) hover:border-(--color-accent)/30 hover:bg-(--color-accent-glow) transition"
            >
              <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path
                  d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0024 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
              GitHub
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://twitter.com/HeimCode"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] px-3 py-2 text-xs text-(--color-ink-muted) hover:text-(--color-ink) hover:border-(--color-accent)/30 hover:bg-(--color-accent-glow) transition"
            >
              <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path
                  d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-4.714-6.231-5.401 6.231H2.744l7.737-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.253 5.622zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
              Twitter / X
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
